# Building the Package{\n}
{\n}
## *NIX/Mac OS X{\n}
{\n}
From the root of the project, simply run{\n}
{\n}
`./gradlew build`{\n}
{\n}
{\n}
## Windows{\n}
{\n}
`./gradlew.bat build`{\n}
{\n}
{\n}
This will compile and assemble the artefacts into the `build/libs/` directory.{\n}
{\n}
Note that this may also run tests (if applicable see the Testing notes){\n}
{\n}
